Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
User startrial
PassCmd "gpg -dq /var/mail/icloud/password.gpg"
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1.2
AuthMechs LOGIN
PipelineDepth 20

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Path /var/mail/icloud/
Inbox /var/mail/icloud/inbox
Trash Trash

Channel icloud-folders
Master :icloud-remote:
Slave :icloud-local:
Patterns "INBOX" "Saved" "Receipts" "Drafts" "Archive" "Sent Messages" "Trash"
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

Group icloud
Channel icloud-folders

